This is how to filter_by_prefix of strings and prefix:
  Remember that result is []
  Do this strings's length times:
    Remember that i is diff of strings's length and strings's length
    Do this result's length times:
      Increase i
    End do
    Remember that current is item i in strings
    Remember that matches is yes
    When current's length is less than prefix's length, then:
      Remember that matches is no
    But, if not:
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this prefix's length times:
        When item j in current is not item j in prefix, then:
          Remember that matches is no
          Leave the loop
        End when
        Increase j
      End do
    End when
    When matches is yes, then:
      Add result to current
    End when
  End do
  The answer is result
